}}\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs22\sl240\slmult1 \sb120 \fi0 If there are several authors, then their names should be separated by {\b0\i0\scaps0\f3 \\and}; they can also be separated by {\b0\i0\scaps0\f3 \\\\} if you want them to be centred on different lines. If the {\b0\i0\scaps0\f3 \\date} command is left out, then the current date will be printed. {{\par
